songs.title: War
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Our world, it's gone
Did we ever grieve or cry now?
I came for help
Did you just really pull my hair out?

[Chorus]
Unleash your war
Unleash war
Your hate will always be my guide
Unleash your war this time again
After all of this, we have no more

[Interlude]

[Chorus]
Unleash your war
Your hate will always be my guide
This time again
After all of this, we have

[Outro]
Unleash your war
